<st-modal
  :title="title"
  v-model="show"
  :footer="null"
  wrapClassName="scroll-modal"
>
  <a-select
    v-model="shelf_status"
    :options="shelfStatusOptions"
    @change="onShelfStatusChange"
    style="width: 200px"
  ></a-select>
  <st-table
    rowKey="id"
    :dataSource="list"
    :columns="columns"
    :scroll="{ y: 230 }"
    :pagination="pagination"
    @change="onPageChange"
    class="mg-t24"
  >
    <template slot="shelf_status" slot-scope="text">{{ text.name }}</template>
  </st-table>
</st-modal>
